    0 => ['[', '‌]', '‌/‌'],
    1 => ['"', '"', '=']
]
~~~

As [Twig](http://twig.sensiolabs.org/doc/tags/embed.html "embed - Documentation - Twig - The flexible, fast, and secure PHP template engine") embed code:

~~~ .xmp.txt
